snippet.title: Best VGM 1172 - For the Frog the Bell Tolls - The Prince's Adventure
snippet.description:
Zelda: Link's Awakening's version : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xJMv0k1TY38

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gameboy
For the Frog the Bell Tolls (1992)
The Prince's Adventure
Kazumi Totaka
